Another piece of advice I give is that if you plan on mingling in with all the roleplayers on FV, it is a good idea to take a brief moment to flesh out the basics of your character, and especially what side he or she supports, if any, in this whole eternal Good vs Evil struggle.<br>
<br>
Have fun and I am sure you will enjoy your time on FV, as this is the best server, with the kindest people of all the available servers. <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center">General <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Stoppelton Starkweather</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--><br>
